data.description: Unbelievable charm in this spacious three bedroom brick home with many original details including arched doorways, original French doors, original ornate windows, fireplace, built-ins, basement, storage, shop, covered deck, and plenty of outdoor space!  This home has been well maintained and cared for, with updates as needed to the flooring and bathrooms that have kept the original personality of the home intact!  There is also a basement that is currently used for a batting cage, as well as a nice backyard area with a covered and screened in deck, wood privacy fence, storage shed, and metal shop. This unique home is a must-see!
